OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fdying out during the evening leaving a
OL,7,Fdry night with clear spells. Turning
OL,8,Fchilly with grass frost developing in
OL,9,Frural areas. The odd mist patch
OL,10,Fforming in the lighter winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FMonday should get off to a
OL,13,Ffine start with some sunshine.
OL,14,FHowever, showers will break out during
OL,15,Fthe day, turning locally heavy and
OL,16,Fthundery. Feeling less chilly with
OL,17,Fgentle winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
