OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,6,Fbright but chilly start on Tuesday
OL,7,Fthen turning wetter and windier from
OL,8,Fthe west through the afternoon and
OL,9,Finto Wednesday. Sunshine and showers
OL,10,Fon Thursday. Temperatures rising
OL,11,Fslightly.
